					<li>
						[4] International Energy Agency (2022). Methane and climate change –
						global methane tracker 2022 – analysis. IEA.
						https://www.iea.org/reports/global-methane-tracker-2022/methane-and-climate-change
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
